<li id="cite_note-Scandinavia-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Scandinavia_9-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Scandinavia_9-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMulder1954" class="citation journal cs1">Mulder, William (August 1954). "Mormons from Scandinavia, 1850-1900: A Shepherded Migration". <i><a href="/wiki/Pacific_Historical_Review" title="Pacific Historical Review">Pacific Historical Review</a></i>. <b>23</b> (3): 227–246. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F3635565">10.2307/3635565</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Pacific+Historical+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Mormons+from+Scandinavia%2C+1850-1900%3A+A+Shepherded+Migration&amp;rft.volume=23&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=227-246&amp;rft.date=1954-08&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F3635565&amp;rft.aulast=Mulder&amp;rft.aufirst=William&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APerpetual+Emigration+Fund" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-Discourses-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Discourses_10-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFYoung1855" class="citation book cs1 cs1-prop-location-test">Young, Brigham (September 16, 1855). <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses/Volume_3/Gathering_the_Poor">"Gathering the Poor"</a>.  Written at Salt Lake City. In Watt, George D. (ed.). <i>Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, and the Twelve Apostles, and Others</i>. London: Orson Pratt (published 1856). pp.&#160;1–6.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Gathering+the+Poor&amp;rft.btitle=Journal+of+Discourses+Delivered+by+President+Brigham+Young%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+and+the+Twelve+Apostles%2C+and+Others&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft.pages=1-6&amp;rft.pub=Orson+Pratt&amp;rft.date=1855-09-16&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FJournal_of_Discourses%2FVolume_3%2FGathering_the_Poor&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APerpetual+Emigration+Fund" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFLeonard1980" class="citation magazine cs1"><a href="/wiki/Glen_M._Leonard" title="Glen M. Leonard">Leonard, Glen M.</a> (January 1980). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/ensign/1980/01/westward-the-saints-the-nineteenth-century-mormon-migration?lang=eng">"Westward the Saints: The Nineteenth-Century Mormon Migration"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Ensign_(LDS_magazine)" title="Ensign (LDS magazine)">Ensign</a></i>. Vol.&#160;10, no.&#160;1. pp.&#160;6–13<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">November 27,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Ensign&amp;rft.atitle=Westward+the+Saints%3A+The+Nineteenth-Century+Mormon+Migration&amp;rft.volume=10&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=6-13&amp;rft.date=1980-01&amp;rft.aulast=Leonard&amp;rft.aufirst=Glen+M.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fstudy%2Fensign%2F1980%2F01%2Fwestward-the-saints-the-nineteenth-century-mormon-migration%3Flang%3Deng&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APerpetual+Emigration+Fund" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-Immigration-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Immigration_12-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMulder1956" class="citation journal cs1">Mulder, William (June 1956). "Immigration and the "Mormon Question": An International Episode". <i><a href="/wiki/The_Western_Political_Quarterly" class="mw-redirect" title="The Western Political Quarterly">The Western Political Quarterly</a></i>. <b>9</b> (2): 416–433. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F444615">10.2307/444615</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Western+Political+Quarterly&amp;rft.atitle=Immigration+and+the+%22Mormon+Question%22%3A+An+International+Episode&amp;rft.volume=9&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=416-433&amp;rft.date=1956-06&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F444615&amp;rft.aulast=Mulder&amp;rft.aufirst=William&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APerpetual+Emigration+Fund" class="Z3988"></span> While the ordinance incorporating the PEFC could hardly prevent immigrants from traveling to Utah if they had other means available, Murray argued that the territory lacked any other legal system to authorize this.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-PEF_Story-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-PEF_Story_13-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-PEF_Story_13-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFLarson1931" class="citation journal cs1">Larson, Gustive O. (September 1931). "The Story of the Perpetual Emigration Fund". <i><a href="/wiki/The_Mississippi_Valley_Historical_Review" class="mw-redirect" title="The Mississippi Valley Historical Review">The Mississippi Valley Historical Review</a></i>. <b>18</b> (2): 184–194. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F1893379">10.2307/1893379</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Mississippi+Valley+Historical+Review&amp;rft.atitle=The+Story+of+the+Perpetual+Emigration+Fund&amp;rft.volume=18&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=184-194&amp;rft.date=1931-09&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F1893379&amp;rft.aulast=Larson&amp;rft.aufirst=Gustive+O.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APerpetual+Emigration+Fund" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
